    "These traces are then mapped back to the source-level code, enabling detailed WCET analysis and optimization using existing tools like RapiTime [75].",
    "The methodology allows engineers to benefit from precise, probe-free timing data while maintaining the ability to understand and optimize the WCET at the source-code level.",
    "The paper demonstrates improvements in WCET estimation accuracy and reduced overheads, emphasizing the practicality of the approach for real-time systems development.",
